# Session artifacts
# Memory lives in docs/ (versionable). Everything under session/ is transient
# (implementation plans, reports, scratch, test checklists) — readable by
# agents when explicitly referenced, but not committed by default.
session/

# Transient implementation plans — readable by agents when explicitly cited,
# but never committed unless the user explicitly asks to version the plan.
# Canonical location: session/implementation/ ; root-level copies are tolerated.
